room_title: Escape room "Operation: Gambit" by Quandary in New Haven
room_description: You and your team of CIA operatives are stationed at a safe house in Seychelles, Africa. For years, intelligence agencies have been trying to identify a shadowy figure known only as Maître D’échecs, or “The Chess Master”, who is rumored to be a shady arms dealer posing as an importer/exporter. Your mission: locate and remove the thumb drive, then escape before the Seychelles SWAT team arrives.
